Class AePartnerLinkValidator

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy.validate.AeAbstractPddIterator
      org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy.validate.AePartnerLinkValidator
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeConstants, IAePredeploymentValidator
public class AePartnerLinkValidator
extends AeAbstractPddIterator

Issue warnings if that any partner links defined in the bpel are not defined in the process deployment descriptor. Fail validation if any partner links (partnerrole or myrole) are present in the pdd BUT NOT in the bpel process.
